<p>Critics claim: Leaked Chinese government records reveal the first case of someone suffering with coronavirus was traced to November 17 - several weeks before Beijing's official record.  </p>

<p>May 3</p>

<p>China claims: They are not to blame for the spread of the outbreak, describing the Wuhan market as a 'victim' and suggesting the virus came from elsewhere.</p>

